name: SetUtils_isEqualSetTest
description: Unit tests for the SetUtils.isEqualSet method, which checks if two sets are equal.

test_cases.name: testIsEqualSet_SameReference
test_cases.description: Tests the isEqualSet method with the same reference for both sets.

test_cases.name: testIsEqualSet_NullAndDifferentSizes
test_cases.description: Tests the isEqualSet method with one set being null and with sets of different sizes.

test_cases.name: testIsEqualSet_EqualContents
test_cases.description: Tests the isEqualSet method with sets having the same contents but in different orders.

test_cases.name: testIsEqualSet_DifferentContents
test_cases.description: Tests the isEqualSet method with sets having different contents.
